        <module id="cnoc">
            <h>cnoc</h>
            <p><g>taigh air <a href="?gd=cnoc">cnoc</a></g>
                <en>a house on a hill</en>
                <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Tha taigh mór air a’ chnoc.</gd>
                        <tr>There is a big house on the hill.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Càit a bheil an taigh mór? Tha an taigh mór air a’ chnoc àrd.</gd>
                        <tr>Where is the big house? The big house is on the tall hill.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 21 [229]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <!--</section>-->
        <!-- <section>
            <h>object</h>-->
        <module id="cat">
            <h>cat</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=cat">cat</a> ann an taigh</g>
                <en>a cat in a house</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>A bheil an cat anns an taigh còmhla ri Seònaid?</gd>
                        <tr>Is the cat in the house with Janet?</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 15 [227]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <!--</section>-->
    </section>

    <section>
        <h>verbs</h>
        <!--  <section>
            <h>object</h>-->
        <module id="ruig">
            <h>ruig</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=ruig">ruig</a> taigh</g>
                <en>... reaches a house</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Bha mi sgìth nuair a ràinig mi an taigh.</gd>
                        <tr>I was tired when I arrived home.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 21</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </module>
        <module id="faag">
            <h>fàg</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=faag">fàg</a> taigh</g>
                <en>... leaves a house</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Bha Màiri agus Seumas anns a’ mhonadh an dé. [...] Dh’ fhàg iad an taigh
                            tràth anns a’ mhadainn.</gd>
                        <tr>Mary and James were on the moor yesterday. [...] They left home early in
                            the morning.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 76</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl>
            </p>
        </module>
        <!--</section>-->
        <!--<section>
            <h>locative</h>-->
        <module id="cluich">
            <h>cluich</h>
            <p><g><a href="?gd=cluich">cluich</a> ann an taigh</g>
                <en>... plays in a house</en> – <xl>
                    <li>
                        <gd>Cha robh sinn a’ cluich anns an taigh.</gd>
                        <tr>We were not playing in the house.</tr>
                        <ref text="617">td. 21 [230]</ref>
                    </li>
                </xl></p>
        </module>
        <!--</section>-->
    </section>

    <section id="other">
        <h>other</h>
        <p>
            <xl>
                <li>
                    <gd>Dé tha ceàrr air a’ ghille seo? Tha a cheann goirt. An robh e anns an sgoil
                        an diugh? Cha robh, bha e anns an taigh fad an latha.</gd>
                    <tr>What is wrong with this boy? His head is sore. Was he in the school today?
                        No, he was in the house all day long.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 20</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha Seònaid anns an taigh.</gd>
                    <tr>Janet is in the house.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 14</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Dé tha a’ chaileag a’ dèanamh anns an taigh?</gd>
                    <tr>What is the girl doing in the house?</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 14 [adapted]</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Cha robh sinn a’ cluich anns an taigh.</gd>
                    <tr>We were not playing in the house.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 21 [230]</ref>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <gd>Tha Seònaid aig an taigh.</gd>
                    <tr>Janet is at home.</tr>
                    <ref text="617">td. 14 [227]</ref>
                </li>
            </xl>
        </p>
    </section>

</module>
